2.5, 625.0, 994.6, 648.1]}, {"text": "The Company has identified the following five approaches to accelerate growth.", "bbox": [179.2, 712.7, 853.8, 735.8]}, {"text": "Table 2 - Approaches to Accelerate Growth", "bbox": [444.6, 770.5, 826.1, 793.6]}, {"text": "1. Delivering a compound annual revenue growth rate of more than 2% through", "bbox": [285.4, 811.4, 950.2, 834.5]}, {"text": "accretive, strategic acquisitions", "bbox": [285.4, 832.2, 546.4, 855.3]}, {"text": "Plus organic growth through:", "bbox": [266.7, 870.7, 513.8, 893.8]}, {"text": "2. Partnering with health plans, IDNs and other risk bearing entities", "bbox": [285.4, 908.3, 849.0, 931.3]}, {"text": "3. Offering the broadest access to diagnostic innovation", "bbox": [285.4, 945.8, 749.3, 968.8]}, {"text": "4. Being recognized as the consumer-friendly provider of diagnostic information", "bbox": [285.4, 979.2, 957.5, 1002.3]}, {"text": "services", "bbox": [285.4, 1000.0, 352.5, 1023.1]}, {"text": "5. Supporting population health with data analytics and extended care services", "bbox": [285.4, 1033.3, 938.7, 1056.3]}, {"text": "1. Growing through acquisitions.  The Company has maintained a strategy since November 2012 to grow revenue", "bbox": [179.2, 1121.0, 1133.7, 1144.1]}, {"text": "each year by a 1-2% compound annual growth rate through accretive, strategic acquisitions.  At our Investor Day in November", "bbox": [104.2, 1146.0, 1166.3, 1169.1]}, {"text": "2018, we announced that, in view of key trends in the clinical testing industry (see the discussion of Key Trends on page13, our", "bbox": [104.2, 1171.0, 1172.2, 1194.1]}, {"text": "strategy now is to generate a compound annual growth rate of more than 2%.  The Company's approach to acquisitions is", "bbox": [104.2, 1196.0, 1118.9, 1219.1]}, {"text": "discussed below on page 7, under the heading Deliver disciplined capital deployment.", "bbox": [104.2, 1221.0, 830.2, 1244.1]}, {"text": "2. Partnering with health plans, IDNs and other risk bearing entities.  To help accelerate growth, we are focusing", "bbox": [179.2, 1271.0, 1130.3, 1294.1]}, {"text": "significant resources on large opportunities to partner with outside entities.  We are deepening our relationships with health", "bbox": [104.2, 1296.0, 1134.5, 1319.1]}, {"text": "plans.  We attempt to build strong partnerships with health plans through engagement, including of the plans, employers,", "bbox": [104.2, 1321.0, 1114.8, 1344.1]}, {"text": "members and clinicians.  We strengthen our relationships with health plans and increase the volume of our services for their", "bbox": [104.2, 1346.0, 1140.7, 1369.1]}, {"text": "members by driving value with employers and providing strong value propositions for members and clinicians. This includes", "bbox": [104.2, 1371.0, 1152.2, 1394.1]}, {"text": "building an information platform to help health plans manage utilization and population health, and enhancing processes to", "bbox": [104.2, 1396.0, 1135.3, 1419.1]}, {"text": "help plans keep laboratory testing in network.  In 2018, the Company established a long-term strategic partnership with", "bbox": [104.2, 1421.0, 1104.0, 1444.1]}, {"text": "UnitedHealthcare, including collaborating on a variety of value-based programs, became a preferred provider to Horizon Blue", "bbox": [104.2, 1446.0, 1160.6, 1469.1]}, {"text": "Cross Blue Shield of New Jersey (with the exception of its managed Medicaid and Dual Eligible Special Needs plan", "bbox": [104.2, 1471.0, 1079.1, 1494.1]}, {"text": "beneficiaries) and became a participating provider to Blue Cross Blue Shield of Georgia.  As a result, the Company began 2019", "bbox": [104.2, 1496.0, 1171.2, 1519.1]}, {"text": "with access to more than 43 million additional insured lives.", "bbox": [104.2, 1521.0, 606.5, 1544.1]}]}